import PyPDF2
pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/18-MassActiv/MassActiv-main/paper.pdf'
reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(pdf_path)

for page in reader.pages[:3]:  # Only first 3 pages for now

print(text[:2000])
